the big city is a 1928 american silent crime film directed by tod browning and starring lon chaney . the film is a lost film . the film was found in ucla film and television archive . the last known print of the film had been sent to australia in the late 1950s . the film was returned to mgm and placed in their vaults where it perished in the same vault fire that also claimed london after midnight in 1967 . a short trailer for the film survives at cinémathèque française in france , but it does not include any footage from the film .